UID:mealplan-20260602-breakfast-4@mealplanner
DTSTAMP:20260601T000323Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260602T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260602T090000
SUMMARY:🍳 Breakfast: Breakfast Burrito
DESCRIPTION:Recipe: Breakfast Burrito\nServings: 2\nPrep: 5 min | Cook: 10 min | Total: 15 min\n\n--- Ingredients ---\n• 4 eggs\n• 2 large flour tortillas\n• 4 slice bacon\n• 0.5 cup shredded cheddar cheese\n• 0.25 cup salsa\n• 1 tbsp butter\n• 1 avocado\n\n--- Steps ---\n1. Cook bacon in a skillet until crispy. Remove and chop.\n2. Whisk eggs, melt butter in the same skillet, and scramble eggs over medium heat.\n3. Warm tortillas in microwave for 15 seconds.\n4. Fill each tortilla with eggs, bacon, cheese, sliced avocado, and salsa.\n5. Fold and roll into burritos. Optional: toast seam-side down in a dry pan for 1 minute.\n\nTip: Meal prep: wrap in foil and freeze. Reheat in microwave 2-3 min.
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
